            "arguments_redacted": {
                "post_type": "page",
                "title": "Neighborhood Cookout Plan",
                "content": "<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Summer Cookout Plan</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Join neighbors for a relaxed summer cookout with grilled favorites, simple sides, cold drinks, and time to catch up outdoors. Everyone is welcome to bring a chair, a dish to share, and their favorite lawn game.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Confirm the date, time, and shared outdoor space for the cookout.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Coordinate the grill, serving tables, plates, napkins, utensils, and trash bags.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Ask neighbors to sign up for sides, desserts, drinks, and lawn games.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:buttons -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-buttons\"><!-- wp:button -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-button\"><a class=\"wp-block-button__link wp-element-button\" href=\"#menu\">View menu</a></div>\n<!-- /wp:button --></div>\n<!-- /wp:buttons -->",
